It wasn't until they got to the airport that Emma discovered they were going to the Big Apple. Alex told her they were going to see a Broadway show that he had promised to take her to earlier that year.

The happy couple visited  famous sites including Times Square but it wasn't until they were standing on Brooklyn Bridge that Alex asked her to be his wife and she accepted.

After the whirlwind long weekend they flew home from Newark airport in New Jersey. But when Alex stepped off the plane in Britain he realised he'd left his phone on the aircraft containing every single picture from the trip.

