The lost phone is a Samsung Galaxy S4 mini in pebble blue. Such is Emma and Alex's hope it will be found they have kept the contract going. 

Alex has refused to block the phone, instead choosing to use an old one, in case one day the lost phone will sync with Google and the missing photos will be found. 

Emma from Birmingham, said: 'After Alex proposed we went back to the hotel we were staying at for a dance and a drink and I remember there was an American lady there who took more pictures of us. I gave her my email address but we never got those photos either.

'Everything is on that phone, pictures of our hands on Brooklyn Bridge after Al proposed, pictures of us with the New York skyline in the background and of us in the Brooklyn River Cafe straight afterwards.

